  "texts": [
    "The discovery that ChatGPT's feedback quality could potentially complement peer feedback highlights its applicability for enhancing feedback practices in higher education.",
    "This holds particular promise for courses with substantial enrolments and essay-writing components, providing teachers with a feasible alternative for delivering constructive feedback to a larger number of students.",
    "(P < 0.05)*, (P < 0.01)**Banihashem et al.",
    "International Journal of Educational Technology in Higher Education (2024) 21:23"
  ]
